title: De Scheepsjongens Van Bontekoe (Johan Fabricius) CDrip mp3
description:
Het verhaal van 'De Scheepsjongens van Bontekoe', voorgelezen door Erik van Muiswinkel, een audioboek van uitgeverij Leopold, 192 kbps cd-rip (14 cd's). Prachtig audiobook. Ik heb er heel veel van genoten.
		

All neatly named and numbered, it took me a while to organize all 60 tracks.

As far as I'm aware this audiobook isn't avaliable for purchase anymore anywhere. It was very hard to get a copy, hence I've uploaded and now am sharing. Please seed to pay it forward.

:-)
